{
  "stem": "14928.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And there was no-- I went to school a lot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I-- when I was 15, when I went to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody together.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a lot of non-Jewish friends when I was in school, because we didn't go to school on Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we really had to have good friends that we went to them Sunday to get our homework, because they wouldn't give us the homework Friday to do.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to go and find it out from the children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had very good non-Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'll tell you, I really never had a Jewish accent in school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I spoke good Polish, and the reason was because since I was little-- I was born 1920.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I must've been-- I don't know when, when we were from the-- I really wasn't in Dubienka, but like next to Dubienka.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was all the time with non-Jewish neighbors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Must've been there one, one house, a Jewish house, with 100 non-Jewish houses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were mixed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think there were Polish and Ukrainian people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I always had non-Jewish friends that were there, because the Jewish-- some children were older, and some like my sisters, you know, they were older.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think mostly the kids were there, so I had the non-Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I always spoke Polish or Ukrainian, I guess Ukrainian most of the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when I came back after my father built up the houses, the home in Dubienka, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was about six years old.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I hardly could speak Yiddish, because I spoke Yiddish, but it was like with a non-Yiddish accent.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I remember the kids laughing at me, the way I speak.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
